tocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\",\nmetadata/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_3/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"akka-protobuf-v3 is Akka's shaded copy of the Google Protocol Buffers v3 Java runtime, relocated under akka.protobufv3.internal for Akka internals. It lets Akka modules parse, build, and serialize protobuf messages without exposing or conflicting with an application's own protobuf-java dependency.\",\nmetadata/io.helidon.service/helidon-service-registry/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Helidon Service Registry provides Helidon's service declaration and registry API, replacing standard service loader patterns with dependency-aware service discovery and lookup. It supports generated service descriptors, scopes, lifecycle activation, qualifiers, interception, and event handling for Helidon applications.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-starter-jackson/index.json:5:    \"replacement\": \"Use the class-bearing dependency org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-jackson:4.0.2 for Spring Boot Jackson integration metadata.\"\nmetadata/com.google.dagger/dagger/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Dagger is a compile-time dependency injection framework for Java and Android applications. It uses annotations to generate type-safe wiring code, reducing runtime reflection and helping applications manage object graphs.\",\nmetadata/org.apache.xbean/xbean-asm7-shaded/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Apache XBean xbean-asm7-shaded repackages and shades ASM 7 classes under the org.apache.xbean.asm7 namespace. It provides an isolated bytecode manipulation dependency for XBean and consumers that need ASM without package conflicts.\",\nmetadata/org.springframework.boot/spring-boot-starter-aop/index.json:4:    \"reason\": \"The published JAR f