branches are brittle and may need test expectation changes, but this is not missing external setup.\",\n    \"If generated tests intentionally cover OGNL's optional security-manager mode or JDK9+ access-handler internals, keep such coverage conditional because those features depend on JVM behavior that changed across recent JDKs.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0c750ff5b6ae5c61016a3f201a5c6c8193b3349ce68db5ef1d\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 804, "output": 1251, "cacheRead": 51712, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53767, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782521864241, "responseId": "resp_0c750ff5b6ae5c61016a3f2008d07481939af13689faf6ebce"}, "toolResults": []}
